*iprutils-2.2.0 (15 Aug 2006)

  15 Aug 2006; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> +iprutils-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Introducing iprutils-2.2.0 ebuild

  27 Mar 2006; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.15.8.ebuild:
  Marking iprutils-2.0.15.8 ppc & ppc64 stable

*iprutils-2.0.15.8 (25 Feb 2006)

  25 Feb 2006; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> +iprutils-2.0.15.8.ebuild:
  Adding iprutils-2.0.15.8.ebuild

  25 Jan 2006; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild:
  Marking iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1 ppc stable for 32bit userland goodness

  03 Nov 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild:
  Marking iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1 ~ppc for 32bit ppc64 userlands

  14 Sep 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild:
  marking iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1 stable for ppc64

  25 Aug 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild:
  Adding a dependancy for hotplug to iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1 so that the
  microcode update utility will work.

*iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1 (22 Aug 2005)

  22 Aug 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> +files/iprdump,
  +files/iprinit, +files/iprupdate, +iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild:
  Adding a new iprutils ebuild called - iprutils-2.0.15.3-r1.ebuild. Changes
  include referencing a new iprdd version, depping sysfsutils-1.3, and the
  addition of 3 init.d scripts.

  16 Aug 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc to iprutils which had applied to ppc64 before only, but with the
  32bit userlands, we'll need to stablize for ppc as well.

  16 Aug 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2.ebuild:
  iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2.ebuild

*iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2 (12 Aug 2005)

  12 Aug 2005; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> +iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2.ebuild:
  Adding iprutils-2.0.13.7-r2 which deps sysfs-utils-1.30. Marking as ~ppc64
  as well because sysfs-utils is ~ for all archs.

  26 May 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Herd name is 'ppc64' not 'gentoo-ppc64'

  09 Mar 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  iprutils-2.0.13.7-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed invalid atoms in *DEPEND.

  06 Mar 2005; Tom Gall <tgall@gentoo.org> +iprutils-2.0.13.7-r1,
  +ChangeLog, +metadata.xml:
  Initial version

*iprutils-2.0.13.7-r1 (06 Mar 2005)

